data.description: Come to Island Reserve!  Welcome home to Unit 10104, this 3 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom condominium / townhome has so much to offer you.  These motivated Sellers are offering a VA assumable loan to those that qualify at 3.9%.  This is a gated community in the perfect location: short golf cart ride to the most beautiful beaches, close to shopping and several restaurants.  There is a an open concept on the first floor.  Kitchen with granite countertops, Stainless-Steel appliances, large island, LVP throughout, large Dining Room that is also open to the Family Room and makes it easy for entertaining.  Head upstairs to the to 3 bedrooms that all have their own bathrooms.  The Master Bedroom has an en-suite with double vanity, soaker tub, stand alone tiled shower and a private balcony.  Two other large bedrooms upstairs with their own full bathrooms, perfect for guests.  The amenities in this complex boast of a HUGE 1 acre pool complex with 3 lanes for lap swimming, rock waterfalls and a hot tub.  There's also indoor basketball, pickleball, large fitness center, community room with pool tables, tables ready to play all your games or do a puzzle, and a theatre room with a projection TV... it has it all!
